info.title: Naukri Job Scraper
info.description: Naukri Job Scraper is an actor that automatically scrapes job postings from Naukri.com. It scrapes details such as job title, company name, experience and salary based on the specified keyword and maximum number of jobs. The collected data can be used for recruitment analysis and market research.
